#FOR BEGINNER
1、CREATE FILES
mode--project
 click-app
      -src
      -main
      -java
new a java class under the java

2、ABOUT SETTINGS
important ones(for start-me)
app:

libs:
      All the jars(it's like zips) put in here

res:
     drawable: pictures
     layout:布局
     values:strings

AndroidManifest.xml:
      a place for registing(程序中定义的四大组件都要在这个文件下注册)
      announcements(可在这个文件添加程序的权限声明)

proguard-rules.pro
      encryption(加密)
      
